There’s something more than the simple physical transformation in this picture I wanna talk to you guys, I wanna talk about the huge mindset difference there’s between these two pictures.
On the left side, I was at the disco. I don’t actually know why I was sitting by myself reading I don’t know what while everybody else was dancing and having fun 🤔 I probably did not feel that good, both physically and mentally. When you under eat, your body craves food and has zero energy. So doing every single thing becomes so difficult you cannot even imagine. Plus, I was so shy and always felt embarrassed about myself that I ALWAYS put myself in the corner just because I was afraid of people judgement. 
Well I don’t have just gained 10 kg in 6 years, I also gained so much confidence. 
At the moment, I actually love partying as much as I love lifting. If you follow me on my personal IG (@corinna.mnt) you know me and my friends enjoy some crazy night quite often 🥂🍻 I’m not saying that you have to get wasted in order to enjoy life (because this is something I still don’t do, I don’t like being sick or so) but just that… life is out of your comfort zone 🤗 And fitness had a big role in this process. Changing my body and my mindset has been the first step to reach a full self confidence and to love my body at 100%. •
